data.description: DISCOVER THE CHARM OF THIS ADORABLE HOME... AS CLOSE TO BEXLEY AS YOU CAN GET FOR $200K!  As you step into the inviting family room, you will notice the beautiful floors which flow throughout the home. The eat-in kitchen features newer appliances and countertops, and the bathroom exudes charm with wainscoting details. Enjoy the large fenced-in yard from your patio. So many updates including new windows '21, furnace '21, A/C '17 and hot water heater '21. White woodwork and doors and newer lighting and fixtures throughout! With an attached garage, this property is a rare find. 10 min from Easton and downtown, 5 minutes from the airport and 20 minutes to Polaris. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this gem yours!
